<root>
  <item>
    <name>asetniop</name>
    <item>
      <name>Note:</name>
      <appendix>To make typing a little easier you should increased the [Simultaneous Keypresses]</appendix>
      <appendix>Delay Threshold in the “Key Repeat” tab to 300 ms.</appendix>
      <appendix>This means you don’t have to press the keys at exactly the same moment.</appendix>
      <appendix>It also means you can’t type too fast or things will get messed up.</appendix>
      <appendix>See what fits you and change it when you get used to asetniop typing.</appendix>
    </item>
    <item>
      <name>Chords</name>
      <appendix>This enables the chords of the qwert-uiop keys.</appendix>
      <identifier>remap.asetniop.chords</identifier>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::Q, KeyCode::W, KeyCode::W</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::Q, KeyCode::E, KeyCode::X</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::Q, KeyCode::R, KeyCode::F</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::Q, KeyCode::U, KeyCode::Q</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::Q, KeyCode::I, KeyCode::KEY_1, ModifierFlag::SHIFT_L</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::Q, KeyCode::O, KeyCode::KEY_9, ModifierFlag::SHIFT_L</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::Q, KeyCode::P, KeyCode::SLASH, ModifierFlag::SHIFT_L</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::W, KeyCode::E, KeyCode::D</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::W, KeyCode::R, KeyCode::C</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::W, KeyCode::U, KeyCode::J</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::W, KeyCode::I, KeyCode::Z</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::W, KeyCode::O, KeyCode::DOT</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::W, KeyCode::P, KeyCode::KEY_0, ModifierFlag::SHIFT_L</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::E, KeyCode::R, KeyCode::R</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::E, KeyCode::U, KeyCode::Y</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::E, KeyCode::I, KeyCode::COMMA</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::E, KeyCode::O, KeyCode::MINUS</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::E, KeyCode::P, KeyCode::QUOTE</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::R, KeyCode::U, KeyCode::B</autogen>
      <autogen>__SimultaneousKeyPresses__ KeyCode::R, KeyCode::I, KeyCode::V</autogen>
